---
title: Polenta Pancakes with Mushroom Gravy and Tangy Arugula Salad
description: These pillowy polenta pancakes are smothered in a creamy mushroom sauce and served on a bed of fresh arugula. The dish is creamy, crispy, tangy, peppery, comforting, AND balanced. In other words, perfection.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mushroom-ragu-with-crispy-polent-0463861c.jpg
